        "Description": "For the &quot;Seven Years of Bad Luck&quot; challenge. The woman should be killed by explosion. The handyman by electrocution. The soldier on the carpet shop roof should be pushed off and killed that way. The soldier in the Shisha Cafe should be drowned in the toilet when he enters the bathroom. And, finally, the shopkeeper should be killed by fire from an oil barrel when he smokes next to it by the shoe shop.",
